  - SliceResult.cs, HighPolyMesh.cs — result container + UV-sphere generator
  - Position + normal + UV0 + tangent supported; cap merged into the body
  submesh with normals along the plane

  Functional tests — 16/16 pass (Assets/MeshCutter/Tests/)
  - Cube, sphere, oblique-plane, no-cap, fully-above, fully-below, area
  conservation, watertightness (Σ triangle area-vectors ≈ 0), Burst-vs-managed
  parity

  Visual validation (Unity MCP scene captures)
  - Sphere cut at y=0 → flat circular cap, two clean hemispheres
  - Cube cut on (1,1,1) plane → hexagonal cap (correct cross-section), two
  pieces
  - Capsule cut on tilted plane → sealed halves

